      "writtenOn": "2019-10-08T18:31:43Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "td.WithEnv sets the environment variables for the process once it is running, but os.Environ needs to be set here so that exec finds the right executable on the PATH.\n\nhttps://golang.org/src/os/exec/exec.go?s\u003d6250:6295#L159\n\nhttps://golang.org/src/os/exec/lp_unix.go?s\u003d928:970#L24\n\nShould td.WithEnv be setting the os.Environ?",
      "parentUuid": "18a8d0ca_4a7f0d38",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 20,
        "startChar": 1,
        "endLine": 30,
